{"tid":1424335,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(勇武入)   兄弟爬山已演變成田雞過河","createTime":"2019-08-06T15:41:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T05:52:31.000Z","uid":178896,"like":17,"dislike":49,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"22e6b2e9ff6004b2604cc94c31136952c3e350f9","tid":1424335,"uid":178896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:41:59.000Z","msg":"大家仲記唔記得8月5日嘅<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">主線係「全港三罷」</span></span>，正常8月6日嘅新聞輿論都應該講緊呢樣。但係，而家「全港三罷」<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">已被勇武行動和不合作運動騎劫</span></span>。你哋有無諗過為咗我地而罷工嘅非勇武人士感受？ 佢地罷工為我哋付出，但係佢哋嘅付出經已付諸流水。<br />\n<br />\n請問大家係咪連自己人嘅感受都唔顧，只係做自己覺得啱嘅嘢？令到<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">整場運動焦點不一</span></span>，由兄弟爬山逐漸演變成田雞過河。如果繼續咁落去，呢場運動注定失敗。<br />\n<br />\n請大家聽下和理非意見，如勇武因被仇恨支配而繼續堅持衝擊，便有可能失去部分和理非支持。抖一抖，唔好急住行動！再討論未來去向，對成件事都好。"},{"pid":"fc2d642f31bee2947631ddd8101d151d4db88b32","tid":1424335,"uid":178896,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:44:04.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"7cbe966ac08756ccd010a6f237b3ca3a41d94e83","tid":1424335,"uid":178896,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:44:22.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"e8287ac9318f12e716ed823abc240667ff00bb40","tid":1424335,"uid":178896,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:44:36.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"43d98db1aa9ef5b0418f6ca93a0a4b761e2fdbd0","tid":1424335,"uid":220690,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:48:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8732246584b8abf6eebe08bf57062b75ed47eaf6","tid":1424335,"uid":53515,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:48:15.000Z","msg":"罷工咪不合作運動囉撚樣 <br />\n<br />\n唔好再覆佢"},{"pid":"969458376c628db1376d344c797de1e60f497e63","tid":1424335,"uid":178896,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8732246584b8abf6eebe08bf57062b75ed47eaf6","tid":1424335,"uid":53515,"like":4,"dislik